{"tid":1602530,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(截至1900) 929香港大事回顧 What's happening in HK on 929?","createTime":"2019-09-29T12:24:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-03T17:38:17.000Z","uid":89898,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"a06c1bbf5512bfb3b3d6aab56d7789859e80013a","tid":1602530,"uid":89898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T12:24:09.000Z","msg":"抱歉小弟英文廢，儘量譯住先，各位手足接力<br />\n煲大支共70大壽前夕，港共大肆打壓港人<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">1) 近距離向立法會議員面部噴射胡椒噴霧</span></strong></span><br />\nDirecting pepper spray at the face of a pan-democratic LegCo member, Heidi Chu, at arm's length<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9d6rzdm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9d6rzdm.jpg&h=6824b7a1&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n《朱凱迪質疑警察即被噴胡椒噴霧》<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1601752/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1601752/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">2) 為打壓港人示威權利，於鬧市亂放TG行戒嚴之實，甚至波及輪椅人士</span></strong></span><br />\nSuppressing freedom of assembly by firing teargas to the crowd in Causeway Bay (downtown of HK) before any conflict happened (while martial law has not been imposed, yet)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5Etmn0V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5Etmn0V.jpg&h=1433d35d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《黑警連輪椅人士都唔放過》<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1601809/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1601809/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">3) 闖入教堂私人地方進行搜捕</span></strong></span><br />\nSearching and arresting teenagers in the Chinese Methodist Church in Wan Chai<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PqzHRW1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPqzHRW1.jpg&h=55946252&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iCsm7vy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiCsm7vy.jpg&h=056f184a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《popo入教堂拉人， 推佢上國際頭條》<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1602176/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1602176/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">4) 疑似布袋鉛彈打中印尼記者右眼 (32:00)</span></strong></span><br />\nTargeting the right eye of an Indonesia journalist with bean bag round<br />\n <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/koransuara/videos/895956760774316/?t=1910\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fkoransuara%2Fvideos%2F895956760774316%2F%3Ft%3D1910&d=AXXoxpexL8qkFRpCGxAvLZbpPLVkgxcsq72qYZiHPFQ%3D&h=4907e1f5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/koransuara/videos/895956760774316/?t=1910</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1trCFEs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1trCFEs.png&h=c612c84f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SWmi9MA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSWmi9MA.jpg&h=b945213d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《17:00 印尼記中眼部中彈，倒地不起，被鎖上手扣》(註：冇上手扣) <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1601996/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1601996/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">5) 疑似催淚彈打中示威者左眼，制服後拒絕急救員進行人道救援</span></strong></span><br />\nTargeting the left eye of a protester, and refusing the first-aider's help after having arrested the protester<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pRWvges.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpRWvges.jpg&h=8f63e305&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《[求認人|危殆] 示威者被擊中，彈殼仍停留在眼部位置，狗拒急救》<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1602253/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1602253/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">6) 人群之中開真鎗 (00:45) </span></strong></span><br />\nFiring real bullet in crowd<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/videos/2422891421365148/?t=46\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstandnewshk%2Fvideos%2F2422891421365148%2F%3Ft%3D46&d=AXXoxpexL8qkFRpCGxAvLZbpPLVkgxcsq72qYZiHPFQ%3D&h=f1dfc3a1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/videos/2422891421365148/?t=46</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aAjTYqp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaAjTYqp.jpg&h=20fc53e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《[突發有片]立場新聞拍到喬裝示威者黑警開真槍》<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1602154/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1602154/page/1</a><br />\n《1742 灣仔莊士敦道警員向示威者開真槍！！》<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1602082/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1602082/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">7) 於特首辦高處向市民開槍，且事前毫無預警</span></strong></span><br />\nFiring teargas (seemingly) to the protesters on the street from the rooftop of CE's office without any warning<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/joshuawongchifung/videos/1306085576226427/?t=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fjoshuawongchifung%2Fvideos%2F1306085576226427%2F%3Ft%3D1&d=AXXoxpexL8qkFRpCGxAvLZbpPLVkgxcsq72qYZiHPFQ%3D&h=4b8ac9ed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/joshuawongchifung/videos/1306085576226427/?t=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">8) 露出笑容，於高處對下方示威者進行狙擊</span></strong></span><br />\nShowing a sinister smile after firing at the protesters<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qYWyYEn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqYWyYEn.jpg&h=75285dc4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《[推上國際] 警察笑住開槍》<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1602083/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1602083/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">9) 偽裝示威者，策動恐襲、放火、煽動暴亂</span></strong></span><br />\nDressing like the protesters and engaging in fights, arsons and riots<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1648246202123798/videos/2518235571585445/?t=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1648246202123798%2Fvideos%2F2518235571585445%2F%3Ft%3D21&d=AXXoxpexL8qkFRpCGxAvLZbpPLVkgxcsq72qYZiHPFQ%3D&h=bcfdfbd7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1648246202123798/videos/2518235571585445/?t=21</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1648246202123798/videos/2468535930094444/?t=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1648246202123798%2Fvideos%2F2468535930094444%2F%3Ft%3D0&d=AXXoxpexL8qkFRpCGxAvLZbpPLVkgxcsq72qYZiHPFQ%3D&h=eccfc276\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1648246202123798/videos/2468535930094444/?t=0</a><br />\n《緊急請注意 20個臥底係廁所換衫 滲入人群》<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1602160/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1602160/page/1</a> <br />\n《蘋果Live有個阿叔睇住卧底放火》<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1602150/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1602150/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">10) 屢次有示威者被捕後昏迷、甚至傳聞有失禁情況</span></strong></span><br />\nSeveral times of arrested protesters being found unconscious, with rumor that one of them was once incontinent<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xjcVspy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxjcVspy.png&h=54bc73a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UkQLPCV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUkQLPCV.png&h=d47fa24b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/ThingsAtHongKong/videos/516664905836539/?t=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FThingsAtHongKong%2Fvideos%2F516664905836539%2F%3Ft%3D3&d=AXXoxpexL8qkFRpCGxAvLZbpPLVkgxcsq72qYZiHPFQ%3D&h=96900cc0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/ThingsAtHongKong/videos/516664905836539/?t=3</a><br />\n《再有人死？》<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1602121/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1602121/page/1</a><br />\n《突發！！黑警又打撚死人呀》<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1601994/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1601994/page/1</a><br />\n《金鐘直播有人比狗打到失去知覺》<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1601980/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1601980/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">11) 屢次對已被制服示威者施以酷刑</span></strong></span><br />\nTorturing the arrested protesters<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ENomnYs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FENomnYs.png&h=58d4c59a&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fk4XFLO.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffk4XFLO.gif&h=2fa4f25d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JktQ0Ms.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJktQ0Ms.gif&h=bd553573&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3mZTYDj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3mZTYDj.jpg&h=52a930a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F9rbLiw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF9rbLiw.jpg&h=7e339792&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《(屌你老母) 將已被捕手足單手址起再扔落地》<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1602017/page/1?post=15\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1602017/page/1?post=15</a><br />\n《警畜酷刑》<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1601971/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1601971/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/hkon9agroup/permalink/3162325380475171/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2Fhkon9agroup%2Fpermalink%2F3162325380475171%2F&d=AXXoxpexL8qkFRpCGxAvLZbpPLVkgxcsq72qYZiHPFQ%3D&h=62db5845\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/hkon9agroup/permalink/3162325380475171/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">12) 公然性侵已被制服女示威者</span></strong></span><br />\nSexually harassing female protester<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f9aLPBm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff9aLPBm.png&h=b1eb2c72&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《突發 防暴公然扯女仔件衫》<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1602186/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1602186/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"a88fe597d9d0d22ce1e4407f3004b1e3e9e6b620","tid":1602530,"uid":89898,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T12:24:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">13) 傳媒聯絡隊動手襲撃圍觀外國人，並反指對方襲警</span></strong></span><br />\nAssaulting a foreigner and framing him for assaulting police (and the blue jacket guy is from PPRB)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia/videos/592705927929974/?t=8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhk.nextmedia%2Fvideos%2F592705927929974%2F%3Ft%3D8&d=AXXoxpexL8qkFRpCGxAvLZbpPLVkgxcsq72qYZiHPFQ%3D&h=a8c5c993\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia/videos/592705927929974/?t=8</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: