a79493558e42f29e02632454fc66aa7cef","tid":1602530,"uid":81084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:22:14.000Z","msg":"#法律知識<br />\n<br />\n警方可以根據警隊條例54(1)對任何行動可疑的人，或54(2)對任何有合理懷疑已犯法的人進行截查。<br />\n<br />\n若你被無理截查，本頻道建議直接引用法律條文質問警方：<br />\n✅根據哪一條警隊條例進行截查；<br />\n✅如果回答54(1)，可追問警方為何你行動可疑；<br />\n✅如果回答54(2)，請追問警方為何懷疑你已經或準備犯法。<br />\n<br />\n案例指出警方應根據客觀事實（時間、地點、現場情況、行為等）作主觀判斷。<br />\n<br />\n‼️截查期間，警方不能要求你解鎖或關閉手機。"},{"pid":"a829c6cff7fd3dd24c27eb1235f47c62a3ccaeb2","tid":1602530,"uid":144942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:26:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31c76d13aba58feaf699ac819203fde2dd8d8cf1","tid":1602530,"uid":46334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T15:28:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d75cdcab905f3ceb2536c0c8e48c59fb438d3104","tid":1602530,"uid":146737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T18:23:42.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"0e76fd4abaec1fa458215cde8702edf6af37f542","tid":1602530,"uid":212845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T18:26:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"09fa34d42d900452df38606b7f069a319f1bad1f","tid":1602530,"uid":268725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T18:28:22.000Z","msg":"仲有恰9個弱能人士<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b65e1a3c5cbe4475e3079ee89e94c8ddbd6a57b","tid":1602530,"uid":14494,"like"